I"Ù0<h1 id="level-up">LEVEL UP</h1>
<p>On level-up, each character gains an â€œAbility Pointâ€, these points can be spent for the following:</p>

<ul>
  <li>2 Skill Points (1AP)</li>
  <li>Feat (1+AP)</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="skills">SKILLS</h1>

<p>A new character starts the game with 15 Skill Point to be distributed. The maximum amount for each skill is equal to 2+level.</p>

